{
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4001_1101_0100_20": "[Name:PlayerNickname ]感覺自己最近\n經常被露莎米奈搭話……",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4001_1001_0200_10": "哎呀，[Name:PlayerNickname ]。\n[SC:Gen Ref=\"255\" M=\"你\" F=\"妳\" ]最近還好嗎？",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4001_1001_0300_10": "有沒有什麼煩惱呢？\n如果有我幫得上忙的地方，\n記得隨時告訴我喔。",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4001_1001_0400_10": "……是嗎。\n沒有什麼問題啊。\n那真是太好了。",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4001_1001_0500_10": "………………",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4001_0301_0600_10": "發生什麼事了嗎？",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4001_0401_0700_10": "……嗯，\n我就跟[SC:Gen Ref=\"255\" M=\"你\" F=\"妳\" ]說說吧。",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4001_0302_0800_10": "抱歉讓妳白擔心了",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4001_0402_0900_10": "不，[SC:Gen Ref=\"255\" M=\"你\" F=\"妳\" ]不用道歉。\n畢竟這是我的問題……",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4001_1001_1000_10": "……老實說，\n自從來到帕希歐之後……",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4001_1001_1100_10": "我感覺孩子們越來越不需要\n我這個監護人來照顧了。",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4001_1001_1200_10": "因為莉莉艾和格拉吉歐\n已經成長得既堅強又茁壯……",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4001_1001_1300_10": "我原本是想默默守護\n那兩個孩子的成長……",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4001_1001_1400_10": "但隨著他們獨立離開我的身邊，\n我的心就像是破了洞般\n感到寂寞不已。",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4001_1001_1500_10": "……該不會，",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4001_1001_1600_10": "我是想透過在一旁默默守護\n和莉莉艾他們年齡相仿的[SC:Gen Ref=\"255\" M=\"你\" F=\"妳\" ]，\n來填補我心中的寂寞……",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4001_1001_1700_10": "……我果然不能再這樣下去了。",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4001_1001_1800_10": "謝謝[SC:Gen Ref=\"255\" M=\"你\" F=\"妳\" ]聽我說這些。\n我感覺調適好心情了。",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4001_1001_1900_10": "抱歉讓[SC:Gen Ref=\"255\" M=\"你\" F=\"妳\" ]配合我的任性，\n那麼我們改天見……",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4002_1101_0100_20": "幾天後……",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4002_1101_0200_20": "[Name:PlayerNickname ]從以太基金會的\n職員口中得知\n「理事長沒有精神」……",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4002_1101_0300_20": "於是前來看看露莎米奈……",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4002_1001_0400_10": "……我身為理事長\n竟然還讓部下擔心，\n真是太不像話了。",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4002_1001_0500_10": "原因恐怕……\n跟我之前說過的事有關。",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4002_1001_0600_10": "我之所以能努力工作至今，\n其中一個理由就是\n為了守護孩子們，",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4002_1001_0700_10": "因為那兩個孩子能依靠的\n只有我這個母親……",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4002_1001_0800_10": "不過，莉莉艾和格拉吉歐\n都已經堅強到能夠獨自踏上旅程了。",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4002_1001_0900_10": "一想到這點，我就不知道自己\n在為了什麼而努力……\n結果對任何事都提不起勁了。",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4002_1001_1000_10": "[Name:PlayerNickname ]，我問[SC:Gen Ref=\"255\" M=\"你\" F=\"妳\" ]……\n[SC:Gen Ref=\"255\" M=\"你\" F=\"妳\" ]覺得父母是什麼呢……",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4002_0301_1100_10": "我希望父母能一直都很帥氣",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4002_0401_1200_10": "帥氣的……",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4002_0302_1300_10": "親子永遠是親子",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4002_0402_1400_10": "永遠……",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4002_1001_1500_10": "……[SC:Gen Ref=\"255\" M=\"你\" F=\"妳\" ]說得沒錯。\n仔細想想，這是很理所當然的事情。",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4002_1001_1600_10": "身為母親與人生的前輩……",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4002_1001_1700_10": "我有責任用自己的背影\n持續向孩子們展現\n「活下去的強大」。",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4002_1001_1800_10": "即便那兩個孩子\n再怎麼長大成人也是如此……",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4002_1001_1900_10": "謝謝[SC:Gen Ref=\"255\" M=\"你\" F=\"妳\" ]，[Name:PlayerNickname ]。",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4002_1001_2000_10": "和[SC:Gen Ref=\"255\" M=\"你\" F=\"妳\" ]聊過之後，\n我察覺到了重要的事情。",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4002_1001_2100_10": "我保護孩子們免於危險的職責\n或許結束了……",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4002_1001_2200_10": "不過我身為母親該做的事情\n已經進到了下一個階段。",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4002_1001_2300_10": "……沒問題，我一定做得到。",
    "episode_event_salon_pasiosalon_date_ch0120_00_lusamine/4002_1001_2400_10": "因為我是露莎米奈呀。"
}
